fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stores moral harmony to the universe. </div><div class="t md9 x6 h37 y4b9 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">OVERVIEW: The Final Judgment </div><div class="t m280 x1a h37 y6b5 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Type </div><div class="t m210 x51 h37 y6b5 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Antitype </div><div class="t m501 x17 h37 y6b6 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lev. 16; 23 </div><div class="t m48f x92 h37 y6b6 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Dan. 7-9, 12 </div><div class="t m2ef x4 h37 y6b6 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Rev. 20:4 </div><div class="t m217 x64 h37 y6b7 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1 Cor. 6:1-3 </div><div class="t m4b7 x83 h37 y6b6 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Rev. 20:11-15 </div><div class="t m27a x25 h37 y6b7 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Matt. 25:31-46 </div><div class="t m245 x6b h37 y6b8 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Day of </div><div class="t m502 x99 h37 y6b9 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Atonement </div><div class="t m367 x92 h37 y6ba ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Investigative </div><div class="t m503 xa1 h37 y6b9 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">phase </div><div class="t m26d x6e h37 y6b8 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Review </div><div class="t m503 x70 h37 y6bb ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">phase </div><div class="t m179 x12 h37 y6ba ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Executive </div><div class="t m504 x54 h37 y6b9 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">phase </div><div class="t m505 x1f h37 y6bc ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE DAY OF ATONEMENT PREFIGURED THE FINAL JUDG-</div><div class="t m2b2 x1f h37 y6bd ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MENT. The Levitical sanctuary is defined by the Bible as a </div><div class="t m1b4 x2b h37 y6bd ff9 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">parable </div><div class="t m3ed x8a h37 y6bd ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and as </div><div class="t m453 x1f h37 y6be ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a </div><div class="t m22c x5f h37 y6be ff9 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">shadow-type. </div><div class="t m506 x29 h37 y6be ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This unique parable or type emphasized three major truths </div><div class="t m19d x1f h37 y6bf ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the gospel: (1) the substitutionary, atoning death of Christ; (2) Christ&apos;s </div><div class="t m507 x1f h37 y6c0 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">priestly mediation; (3) the final judgment. </div><div class="t m42a x17 h37 y6c1 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The sanctuary rituals and symbols were intended to enable Israel to </div><div class="t m3b3 x1f h37 y6c2 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">understand the gospel (Heb. 4:1, 2). The plan of salvation—including the </div><div class="t m37e x1f h37 y6c3 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">judgment—is not being carried out to inform God. He knows all things. </div><div class="t m220 x1f h37 y6c4 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The plan was laid, and is progressively unfolding, in order to bring the in-</div><div class="t m2ec x1f h37 y6c5 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">habitants of the universe into agreement with God&apos;s view of sin and </div><div class="t m1d8 x1f h37 y6c6 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">righteousness. Heavenly beings as well as the human family are interested </div><div class="t m380 x1f h37 y6c7 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in the issues involved. (See 1 Peter 1:10-12; Eph. 3:8-11.) At the end of </div><div class="t m508 x1f h37 y6c8 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">44 </div><div class="t m509 x98 h4d y6c9 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">g7</div><div class="t m50a x9b h4d y6c9 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">.</div><div class="t m1d7 x97 h4d y6c9 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3 </div><div class="t m50b x98 h4d y6ca ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">W1 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
